Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.34,0:01:57.80,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5}第二 冲破蛋壳 世界将无限宽广
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.52,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}你扣动正义的扳机
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.48,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}散发异样的情感 让我厌恶
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.56,0:02:14.86,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}你总是找着悲伤借口
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.86,0:02:18.24,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}扮演着女主角 让我憎恨
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.45,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}泪水根本不适合你吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.87,0:02:26.87,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A2F2&\blur5\3a&H24&\bord2}镜子里真正的我
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.54,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}一事无成且原地踏步
